data.description: Fantastic property with DOUBLE PANED WINDOWS, NEW ROOF, including NEW  HURRICANE SKY LIGHTS (2023), ensuring excellent structural integrity.  New flooring in front bedrooms, and back bathroom, remodeled hall bathroom, new smart stainless steel stove, stainless refrigerator and dishwasher add a modern touch, along with fresh interior and exterior paint. Tiled throughout with fresh laminate in the two front bedrooms. Large Privacy fenced backyard with mature trees. Wooded lot next door and across the street, and no neighbors behind as it backs up to a canal - lots of privacy. Close to Heritage Parkway, I-95 and 192.
